data.description: Nestled within the sought-after enclave of Stone Oak, this exquisite two-story retreat beckons with its blend of charm and functionality. Boasting 3 bedrooms and a spacious game room upstairs, complemented by a private primary bedroom downstairs, this home offers versatility to suit your dynamic lifestyle.    Conveniently located within walking distance to an elementary school, education and ease converge effortlessly. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open floor plan, perfect for both entertaining and daily living. The primary bedroom, tucked away on the main level, provides a serene haven for relaxation.    Outside, mature oak trees dot the landscape, lending shade and character to the backyard oasis. Dive into luxury with a heated pool featuring enchanting multicolored lights and soothing water features, accompanied by a rejuvenating spa installed in 2022. The newly laid turf creates a lush setting for outdoor enjoyment.    Pet lovers will appreciate the custom dog room beneath the stairs, showcasing tile flooring that echoes the adjacent laundry room's aesthetic.    Inside, revel in the absence of carpet as gleaming wood floors span the residence, while tiled bathrooms and kitchen offer practicality and elegance. The kitchen has been tastefully upgraded with granite countertops, an island boasting quartz, and a custom pantry, enhancing culinary experiences.    Experience the epitome of comfort and convenience in this meticulously crafted abode. Schedule a showing today and discover the endless possibilities awaiting you in this tranquil retreat amidst the allure of Stone Oak living.
